{"name":"Alberto Valero","size":"medium","type":"humanoid","tag":"IronVale, IronCore","alignment":"Neutral Good","hitDice":"15","armorName":"other","shieldBonus":0,"natArmorBonus":10,"otherArmorDesc":"15 (Body Armor)","speed":"30","burrowSpeed":"0","climbSpeed":"0","flySpeed":"0","hover":false,"swimSpeed":"0","customHP":false,"customSpeed":false,"hpText":"22 (5d8)","speedDesc":"30 ft.","strPoints":"8","dexPoints":"12","conPoints":"12","intPoints":"20","wisPoints":"18","chaPoints":"14","blindsight":"0","blind":false,"darkvision":"0","tremorsense":"0","truesight":"0","telepathy":0,"cr":"5","customCr":"1 (200 XP)","customProf":2,"isLegendary":false,"legendariesDescription":"The monster can take 3 legendary actions, choosing from the options below. Only one legendary action option can be used at a time and only at the end of another creature's turn. The monster regains spent legendary actions at the start of its turn.","isLair":false,"lairDescription":"When fighting inside its lair, the monster can invoke the ambient magic to take lair actions. On initiative count 20 (losing initiative ties), the monster can take one lair action to cause one of the following effects:","lairDescriptionEnd":"The monster can't repeat an effect until they have all been used, and it can't use the same effect two rounds in a row.","isMythic":false,"mythicDescription":"If the monster's mythic trait is active, it can use the options below as legendary actions for 1 hour after using {Some Ability}.","isRegional":false,"regionalDescription":"The region containing the monster's lair is warped by the creature's presence, which creates one or more of the following effects:","regionalDescriptionEnd":"If the monster dies, the first two effects fade over the course of 3d10 days.","properties":[],"abilities":[{"name":"Chrono Step","desc":"Instead of manually walking, [MON] teleports using his watch. This does not trigger opportunity attacks."}],"actions":[{"name":"Comptrolux .45","desc":"[MON] fires a high-tech pistol that does all the calculations for him. [INT ATK] to hit, range 30/60 ft. _Hit:_ [INT 1D10] piercing damage."}],"bonusActions":[{"name":"Radar Scanner","desc":"[MON] reveals all creatures within a 30ft. radius."},{"name":"Steel Defender","desc":"[MON] may command his Steel Defender to take an action."}],"reactions":[{"name":"Force Field","desc":"[MON] raises up a force field and increases his AC by 5 against one attack."}],"legendaries":[],"mythics":[],"lairs":[],"regionals":[],"sthrows":[{"name":"con","order":2},{"name":"wis","order":4}],"skills":[{"name":"history","stat":"int"},{"name":"insight","stat":"wis"},{"name":"investigation","stat":"int"},{"name":"perception","stat":"wis"}],"damagetypes":[],"specialdamage":[],"conditions":[],"languages":[],"understandsBut":"","shortName":"Valero","pluralName":"","doubleColumns":true,"separationPoint":1,"damage":[]}